1. Project Name
AI Travel Planner

2. Description

AI Travel Planner is a smart web-based application that helps users plan trips easily using artificial intelligence.
Users can enter their destination, travel days, and preferences, and the system generates a personalized travel plan with places to visit, schedules, and suggestions.

The project is built using modern web technologies with AI integration to automate trip planning and improve user experience.

3. Features

• User authentication (Login & Signup)
• AI-powered travel plan generation
• Destination-based itinerary creation
• Dynamic travel recommendations
• Clean and responsive UI
• Backend API support
• Easy to extend for future features

4. Tech Stack
  Frontend
    React.js
    HTML, CSS, JavaScript
  Backend
    Python
    FastAPI
    AI Integration
    OpenAI / LLM-based response generation
  Database
    SQLite / MongoDB (optional)

6. Project Structure
    Frontend
      UI components
      Pages (Home,Planner)
      API integration
    Backend
      API routes
      Authentication logic
      AI request handling
      Travel planner logic

7. How to Run the Project
  Backend Setup
    Clone the repository
    Navigate to backend folder
    Install dependencies
    pip install -r requirements.txt
    Run the server
    uvicorn main:app --reload
  Frontend Setup
    Navigate to frontend folder
    Install dependencies
    npm install
    Start frontend
    npm start
8. How It Works
    User signs up or logs in
    User enters travel details
    AI processes input
    Travel plan is generated
    User receives itinerary and suggestions
9. Future Enhancements
• Hotel and flight booking integration
• Map-based trip visualization
• Budget-based planning
• Multi-language support
• User trip history
• Downloadable travel plan PDF

10. Project Status
Completed – Ready for improvement and deployment

